Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透是饭团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又发生什么事情了吗 你是怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人又说你什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.46,0:02:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为还有我 只有我爱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是爱着你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个百分之百的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的 我一点也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对 其实你很害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一天内才要确认好几次看看念珠在不在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我最骄傲的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那为何不让我出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你长得太可爱了 所以不想让别人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是觉得丢脸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我最爱你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你 妈妈连死都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么老说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实你根本不认同我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会说一些做母亲的冠冕堂皇的话而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.47,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈比谁都要爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道我们…就只能逃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只能逃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受够这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.78,0:04:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 你快说 快点说出实话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你现在想的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点说实话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想说泄气话就说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透你该照你的个性去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气馁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.09,0:05:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说些任性的话也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 什么力量也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很怕这样的阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.70,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后我也想要和你一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起…生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.51,0:06:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起吃饭 一起上学 一起烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也希望你能听我的任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想听听你的泄气话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我想和你一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.25,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必…对我付出全部的爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得害怕…也不要紧的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实会害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正是看清真正的我的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我母亲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会用爱情这两个字来敷衍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不想真正看清我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我多希望她能和我一起想、一起烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算不爱我这丑陋的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以…和我一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直以为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都不会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.78,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁都不会跟我说这种话的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讲出我现在最想听的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.72,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么像你这样的女孩会待在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会为我哭泣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.76,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要…谢谢你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么连声招呼都不打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…虽然现在还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.01,0:10:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但总有一天 "师父你是我的父亲"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定能挺起胸膛对任何人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定…会变成这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.58,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是个要人照顾的儿子呢 夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能做的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要照你原本的方法去做就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热腾腾的白饭淋上纳豆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一大早就这么有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 今天吃梭鱼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天我想去看慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.72,0:12:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人剩下的日子不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.93,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他背负着我们整个诅咒的"核"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那是出生时就决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他自己也无力改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我们能做的事就是顺从他的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.64,0:13:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于你 我不希望你和他接触太多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 波鸟吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在要过去 可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只我啦 还有小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真有胆量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底来干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么会不知道 只是不敢说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我帮你说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是想说希望大家都能一起在那个家和睦地生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.78,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要让你对于介入草摩家一事后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你痛苦 一定要让你痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你憔悴消瘦不成人形 然后跪在我面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也给我搞清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要离开草摩家根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不可以违背我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点说"请您原谅我"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说"我再也不会介入草摩家"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:16:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您一定很痛苦吧 慊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从您生下来那一天就被宣告了死的日期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.00,0:16:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是多么的痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 你知道什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种恐惧是常人无法想像的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.01,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫吴、由希和阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.35,0:16:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定也都很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至连波鸟也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人您死了的话 大家会很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会非常难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.76,0:16:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.93,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会难过呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是因为我才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们根本希望我早点消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了死而诞生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是命中注定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁能决定这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明明活得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活着？这样子算是活着吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命中注定的 注定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又没叫你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不知道你母亲死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴 别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟 快把这女人的记忆消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.81,0:17:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很希望你能一直活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你能一直看着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭了 你别再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不知道什么是诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够和慊人相遇我真的感到很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和大家相遇我绝对不会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能多多聆听慊人你的心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你生气也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是痛苦或悔恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都很想知道慊人的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是活着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.55,0:19:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.79,0:20:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭老鼠 到底发生什么事 你快点说清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.56,0:20:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我好像太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是关于我肚子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去之后我一定会告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.45,0:20:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去之后来决胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经有心理准备啦 可别让我觉得太无趣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 话还没说完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还真有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在某方面也挺有精神的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那倒是 虽然我什么也帮不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没结束呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好今后会找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底要找什么如果能由我们决定就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.84,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我们无法成功 后面也还有人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得也是 慢慢来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 快点走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩菜剩饭也没关系 快点弄东西给我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我肚子好饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 你有在天上看着我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有时候我会想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我会往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.29,0:21:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都会往前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.00,0:21:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会走到比这里更远的地方

